    "title": "Looking for Financial Analyst at Bank of India Holdings Services",
    "description": "Bank of India Holdings Services invites applications from qualified candidates for the position of Financial Analyst at our Noida location. This role offers excellent career advancement prospects.\n\nAbout Bank of India Holdings Services:\nBank of India Holdings Services is a leading organization in the On-site sector, committed to excellence, innovation, and employee growth. We offer a dynamic work environment where talent is recognized and rewarded.\n\nKey Responsibilities:\n• Monitor market trends and provide investment recommendations\n• Implement and maintain internal controls and audit procedures\n• Process payroll and manage employee reimbursements\n• Maintain general ledger and ensure accurate bookkeeping\n• Monitor financial performance against targets and provide variance analysis\n• Prepare MIS reports for senior management review\n• Prepare annual reports and investor presentations\n\nRequired Skills & Qualifications:\n• B.Ed / M.Ed from a recognized institution\n• 0-1 years of relevant experience\n• Proficiency in Risk Management\n• Proficiency in Financial Modeling\n• Proficiency in SQL\n• Proficiency in VBA\n• Proficiency in IFRS\n• Proficiency in SAP FICO\n• Proficiency in GST\n• Proficiency in Bloomberg Terminal\n\nWork Mode: On-site - Work from our office\n\nWhat We Offer:\n• Referral bonus program\n• Work-from-home flexibility\n• Annual performance appraisal\n• Transportation and conveyance allowance\n• Maternity and paternity leave\n• Competitive salary with performance-linked incentives\n• Salary Range: 2.5 LPA - 6 LPA per annum\n\nLocation: Noida, Uttar Pradesh, India\n\nIf you are excited about this opportunity, apply now and take the next step in your career journey with Bank of India Holdings Services!",
